N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4403.1 - Condition of operation

State Regulations
A condition precedent to the exercise of authority by any
corporation is strict compliance with each rule, regulation, decision, directive, or order of the commission. The commission may suspend or revoke in
whole or in part the operating authority of a corporation. Notes
